&lt;li&gt;Minimum of&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;8-10+ years of progressive agency experience&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;in account management, with at least&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;3-5 years specifically in a Senior Account Director&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;or equivalent leadership role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive and proven experience managing large, complex international accounts within the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;FMCG (Fast-Moving Consumer Goods) and Beauty sectors is absolutely essential.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
